7
00:00:31,990 --> 00:00:34,617
Yeah. Just go with your gut.

8
00:00:40,165 --> 00:00:42,125
<i>Howard's End</i> all the way down, huh?

9
00:00:42,292 --> 00:00:44,085
I just love Emma Thompson.

10
00:00:44,252 --> 00:00:46,838
-Who doesn't?
-She's so pragmatic.

11
00:00:47,047 --> 00:00:48,798
Yeah, well, fingers crossed.

12
