-Hey, hey.
-Hey. How'd we do?

13
00:00:55,180 --> 00:00:57,891
This is everything from two.

14
00:00:58,058 --> 00:01:00,101
And I even got Chloe to throw in.

15
00:01:00,268 --> 00:01:04,355
Many have tried to argue
with Kim Wexler, all have failed.

16
00:01:04,522 --> 00:01:06,858
I'm headed up to four.
You got anything?

17
00:01:07,025 --> 00:01:08,234
Yeah.

18
00:01:09,903 --> 00:01:12,947
-And I'll do three.
-Already done.

19
00:01:13,281 --> 00:01:15,700
