It's called being friendly.
It's great for morale.

22
00:01:21,956 --> 00:01:24,542
It is great for wasting time.

23
00:01:24,709 --> 00:01:26,503
-That too.
-Okay, so....

24
00:01:26,669 --> 00:01:29,172
