58
00:03:04,893 --> 00:03:06,144
How's it going?

59
00:03:06,311 --> 00:03:08,354
Very well, thank you.

60
00:03:08,521 --> 00:03:10,315
Congratulations, again, on Isaacson.

61
00:03:10,523 --> 00:03:13,026
-Well.... Heh, heh.
-I'm sure that you considered it.

62
00:03:13,193 --> 00:03:16,237
