would have been liable...

63
00:03:16,404 --> 00:03:18,990
...under the continuing enterprise
exception as well?

64
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:21,117
That's right. Yeah, we looked into that.

65
00:03:21,284 --> 00:03:22,994
