229
00:15:10,034 --> 00:15:11,869
<i>The lawyer?</i>

230
00:15:12,036 --> 00:15:14,121
Yeah. What can I do for you?

231
00:15:14,288 --> 00:15:15,915
<i>My name's Brett Dunst.</i>

232
00:15:16,081 --> 00:15:17,791
<i>I think you did my aunt's will?</i>

233
00:15:17,958 --> 00:15:21,795
<i>At least, that's what it says here.</i>
<i>She-- She died.</i>

234
00:15:21,962 --> 00:15:24,715
-I'm sorry to hear that.
-<i>Thanks. I'm the executor...</i>

235
00:15:24,882 --> 00:15:28,427
<i>...and I've distributed all her stuff,</i>
<i>but there's some finer details...</i>

236
00:15:28,594 --> 00:15:31,889
<i>...in this that are tricky.</i>
<i>I thought you could help me with those.</i>

237
00:15:32,056 --> 00:15:33,432
Who was your aunt?

238
00:15:33,599 --> 00:15:36,060
<i>Geraldine Strauss.</i>

239
00:15:36,560 --> 00:15:40,147
Oh, Mrs. Strauss passed away? How?

240
00:15:40,314 --> 00:15:45,235
<i>She, uh-- She went in her sleep</i>
<i>a couple weeks ago. Heart failure.</i>

241
00:15:45,402 --> 00:15:46,862
Oh.

242
00:15:48,614 --> 00:15:50,824
<i>-Hello?</i>
-I'm....

